MDK2 *with CDDA*
Region    : USA/NTSC
Date      : February 17, 2001
CD Required    : 80min

Descrition:
    None needed, you all know this kickass game. :)

Notes:
Finally this is released with CDDA! You may be thinking "wasn't this released already?", the answer is NO. Someone released it with "dummy tracks" for reasons way beyond me. A little bit of work had to go into this, but what release doesnt require work? Anyways, CDDA works great unlike so many other releases I have seen lately. If you've never played this game give it a shot, it's great. By the way, the music in this game is actually pretty cool, so enjoy it and have fun with this release. 